com.bandyer.core_av.subscriber

Class Subscriber

  • com.bandyer.core_av.subscriber.Subscriber

  • public class Subscriber

    This class represents a subscriber to a stream. A subscriber is someone who is in read-only mode on a stream.

    The first step to use the subscriber is create it, by instantiating with a stream it refers to.
